RE_Didier_Messens-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ANDRE_DIAS_NOBRE_Didier_Messens-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ANDRE_DIAS_NOBRE_Didier_Messens-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 2024 年英国最畅销的黑胶唱片和单曲已经揭晓，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher)</a>分别名列榜首。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="807" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-albums-2024-3818995"><b>2024 年 50 张最佳专辑</b></a></li></ul><p>斯威夫特的第 11 张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-the-tortured-poets-department-lyrics-tracklist-3619454">The Tortured Poets Department</a> 》以 112,000 张密纹唱片销量（来自<a href="https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/the-official-best-selling-vinyl-albums-and-singles-of-2024/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>官方排行榜公司</i></a>）的成绩位居年度黑胶唱片排行榜榜首。没有任何一张专辑在本世纪发行的第一年就卖出了如此多的销量，其中 66,000 张的销量是在发行的第一周发生的。</p><p>这是斯威夫特连续第三年在英国黑胶唱片排行榜上名列前茅——2023 年，《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-1989-taylors-version-review-lyrics-tracklist-3522001">1989（泰勒版本）</a> 》位居第一，而 2022 年，《<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-midnights-review-3332805">午夜</a>》占据榜首。</p><p>这两张专辑也在 2024 年的排行榜上占有一席之地，前者排名第 20 位，后者排名第 38 位。斯威夫特的其他三张专辑——《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/taylor-swift-lover-review-2541084">Lover</a> 》（29 位）、《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/taylor-swift-folklore-album-review-2713965">Folklore</a> 》（30 位）和《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/taylor-swift-evermore-review-2835933">Evermore</a> 》（36 位） – 也在 2024 年前 40 名中占有一席之地。 </p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3619963" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Taylor-Swift-Tortured-Poets-Department.jpg" alt="泰勒·斯威夫特" width="3000" height="3000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Taylor-Swift-Tortured-Poets-Department.jpg 3000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Taylor-Swift-Tortured-Poets-Department-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Taylor-Swift-Tortured-Poets-Department-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Taylor-Swift-Tortured-Poets-Department-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Taylor-Swift-Tortured-Poets-Department-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Taylor-Swift-Tortured-Poets-Department-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Taylor-Swift-Tortured-Poets-Department-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /></p><p>排名第二的是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a> 1994 年经典首张专辑《Definitely Maybe》 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-30th-anniversary-reissue-of-definitely-maybe-featuring-unheard-versions-3758723">30 周年纪念重新发行版</a>。自 9 月份发行以来，这张重新发行的专辑销量超过 50,000 张，并在总体专辑排行榜上排名第一。</p><p> 2024 年一些最热门的专辑进入了前五名，其中<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">Chappell Roan</a>的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/chappell-roan-the-rise-and-fall-of-a-midwest-princess-review-debut-album-radar-3499595">The Rise And Fall Of A Midwest Princess</a> 》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">Sabrina Carpenter</a>的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sabrina-carpenter-short-n-sweet-review-3787293#:~:text=As%20'Short%20n'%20Sweet',largely%20gets%20the%20job%20done.">Short N&#39; Sweet</a> 》和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c">Fontaines DC</a>的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/fontaines-d-c-romance-review-3784445">Romance</a> 》均入围。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish)</a>的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/billie-eilish-hit-me-hard-and-soft-review-tracklist-lyrics-3756826">Hit Me Hard And Soft</a> 》排名第六。</p><p> 2024 年黑胶唱片排行榜的其余部分中，经典唱片如<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fleetwood-mac">Fleetwood Mac</a>的《Rumours》（排名第七）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/amy-winehouse">Amy Winehouse</a>的《Back To Black》（排名第 13）与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a>等新时尚引领者并肩。的“<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-review-lyrics-tracklist-3762875">小子</a>”（10）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">最后的晚宴的</a>“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-last-dinner-party-prelude-to-ecstasy-album-review-radar-3577784">狂喜前奏</a>”（12）。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-cure">The Cure</a>的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-cure-songs-of-a-lost-world-review-lyrics-3801637">Songs Of A Lost World</a> 》进入前十名，排名第 8，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">酷玩乐队</a>的最新唱片《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/coldplay-moon-music-review-3798469">Moon Music</a> 》也是如此（第 9 名）。</p><p>在榜单的下方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/radiohead">Radiohead</a>的《OK Computer》（第 27 名）、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jeff-buckley">Jeff Buckley</a>的《Grace》（第 24 名）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-stone-roses">The Stone Roses</a>的同名首张专辑（第 22 名）等常青歌曲继续占据席位。</p><p>在 2024 年黑胶单曲榜上，利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher) 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/john-squire">约翰·斯奎尔 (John Squire)</a>的《Just Another Rainbow》位居榜首，领先于查普尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan) 的热门歌曲《Good Luck, Babe!》。以及诺亚·卡汉 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noah-kahan">Noah Kahan)</a>的《Stick Season》，这是今年最热门的歌曲。</p><p>与专辑排行榜一样，复古单曲遍布整个黑胶单曲排行榜，包括 Oasis 的“Supersonic”(4) 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wham">Wham!</a>的《去年圣诞节》(5)，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sophie-ellis-bextor">索菲·埃利斯-贝斯特 (Sophie Ellis-Bextor</a> ) 的《舞池谋杀案》将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sophie-ellis-bextor-calls-murder-on-the-dancefloor-revival-spectacular-3566559">2024 年</a>重演，年终排名第 25 位。</p><p>年度其他热门单曲也出现在榜单中，包括 Sabrina Carpenter 的《Espresso》（第 10 名）、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a>的《Houdini》（第 11 名）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ariana-grande">Ariana Grande</a>的《Yes, And》。</p><h2> <strong>2024 年官方十大最畅销黑胶专辑</strong></h2><ol><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid="805" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1)&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><strong>泰勒·斯威夫特 – 《受折磨的诗人部》</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid="805" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1)&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><strong>绿洲——“绝对有可能”</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid="805" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1)&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-s